- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is a possible category as the paper deals with the behavior of a distributed system (replicated list object) under different schedules of operations/messages.
- cs.CC (Computational Complexity) is a less likely category as the paper does not focus on the complexity analysis of any algorithm or data structure.
